text:
Save this post 💚🌻It’s finally spring! We’re rolling out our free spring/summer markets and events. 🤩 

🥕 Farmers Market : April 22nd — December 19th. Every Monday and Thursday 3-7pm at the Grove St PATH Plaza 

🏷️Handmade Market : May 1st — September 8th. This open air art bazaar happens every Wednesday 3-8pm and Saturday 12-6pm at the Grove St PATH Plaza. @handmademarket_jc 

🎸Groove on Grove : May 1st — August 28th. Free live music performance by local talent. Every Wednesday 6-9pm at the Grove St PATH Plaza.

🪗Applause in the Plaza : June 14th — August 23rd. Free live music performance by local talent. Every Friday 6-8pm at the Newark Ave Pedestrian Mall stage (164 Newark Ave).

🎡All about downtown street fair : September 21st. 300+ local businesses to explore, shop and drink. Rides, beer gardens, live music and so much more. 12-8pm from Grove St to Coles St in Downtown Jersey City. 

All of these events are FREE to attend 💚🙌 
📍Historic Downtown Jersey City, New Jersey. 
Which ones are you looking forward to? 🎉

P.S we’re still accepting vendors! Click the link in our bio, or visit jcdowntown.org/events to apply.
